                        <div data-hook="review-collapsed" aria-expanded="false" class="a-expander-content reviewText review-text-content a-expander-partial-collapse-content" style="padding-bottom: 20px;"> <span>A great compact mini pc with great speed. I purchased this unit to replace an old desktop I had in my garage. It is quite an amazing piece of tech for the size. I will probably buy another with more storage and ram to replace our old Lenovo desktop in our home office.<br>The problem I had was the network adapter was stuck at 100/100 mps for the ethernet. This is a 1 GB adapter. I could get 140mps on wifi but ethernetstpped short of 100. I called support and spent about an hour with a nice fellow named Melvin. We did some resets and changed the adapter from auto negotiate to 1 GB speed. We also tried another cat 5e cable that I had new on hand to no avail. Didn't help. We left it at that while he would contact others to help out. In the meantime I decided to get some cat 6 ethernet cable to replace the cat5e that I was using. That FIXED the problem. I got 960mps download on the first speed test. Upload is maxed at 108mps by the internet provider.<br>Kin from the support team followed up with emails and I would say that this company (Kamrui) really does care about their products.<br>I did not rate gaming as I am not a gamer.<br>Thanks<br>Update: The Cat5e cables that I was using were quite old and I believe defective. I tried another Cat5e that went to my home office and it worked fine. Was able to get 947 mps. So the quality of the cable was the issue.<br>Thanks</span>

                     <div class="a-row a-spacing-small review-data">

                      <span data-hook="review-body" class="a-size-base review-text">

                       <div data-a-expander-name="review_text_read_more" data-a-expander-collapsed-height="300" class="a-expander-collapsed-height a-row a-expander-container a-expander-partial-collapse-container" style="max-height: none; height: 300px;">

                        <div data-hook="review-collapsed" aria-expanded="false" class="a-expander-content reviewText review-text-content a-expander-partial-collapse-content" style="padding-bottom: 20px;"> <span>I bought this Mini PC for my grandmother as a surprise gift as her old pc had failed.<br><br>I choose this as the N95 CPU is very low power and should work well for her needs.<br><br>Changes I have made<br>- I swapped out the 8GB ram stick for a 16GB ram stick, this was super easy to do as the top pops right off and only required me to remove one screw for the top cover, after this, there are 4 screws holding the Sata drive slot and I was able to easily remove and replace the install DIMM<br><br>- I did not detect any malicous activity or junkware on the base operating system. If you plan to reimage and use the Window key that came with the system please ensure to connect to the network and link the key to your microsoft account<br><br>- For the price I am happy with this Mini PC and I feel it will meet my grandparent's needs well.<br><br>Couple of caveats to be aware of<br><br>- HDMI for this unit only supports 1440P 60HZ maximum. (I would love to see this improved in a newer model<br>- the model I picked up does not have USBC, I would love to see usbC with displayport out instead of HDMI or displayport or VGA as this would be more flexible.<br>- I could not get the memory to clock up to 3200mhz (Performance change should be negligible though<br>- If you plan to run linux, make sure to run as new of a kernel as possible as the N100/N95 chip is very new.<br><br>Tips:<br>Ensure to install the codec packs from the windows store to allow for the built in hardware decoder to work (AV1 H265 MPEG 2 and HEVC) This will ensure that youtube and video streaming are as smooth as possible.</span> 

                        </div>

     <script type="text/javascript">



function prefetchTYPAssets() {

    var imageAssets = new Array();

    var jsCssAssets = new Array();

      imageAssets.push("https://m.media-amazon.com/images/G/01/x-locale/common/buy-buttons/review-1-click-order._CB485945748_.gif");

      imageAssets.push("https://m.media-amazon.com/images/G/01/x-locale/common/buttons/continue-shopping._CB485936085_.gif");

      imageAssets.push("https://m.media-amazon.com/images/G/01/x-locale/common/buy-buttons/thank-you-elbow._CB485935881_.gif");

      imageAssets.push("https://m.media-amazon.com/images/G/01/x-locale/communities/social/snwicons_v2._CB485949224_.png");

      imageAssets.push("https://m.media-amazon.com/images/G/01/checkout/assets/carrot._CB485936886_.gif");

      imageAssets.push("https://m.media-amazon.com/images/G/01/checkout/thank-you-page/assets/yellow-rounded-corner-sprite._CB485934148_.gif");

      imageAssets.push("https://m.media-amazon.com/images/G/01/checkout/thank-you-page/assets/white-rounded-corner-sprite._CB485935362_.gif");



    // pre-fetching image assets

    for (var i=0; i<imageAssets.length; i++) {

       new Image().src = imageAssets[i];

    }

    // pre-fetching css and js assets based on different browser types

    var isIE = /*@cc_on!@*/0;

    var isFireFox = /Firefox/.test(navigator.userAgent);

    if (isIE) {

      for (var i=0; i<jsCssAssets.length; i++) {

        new Image().src = jsCssAssets[i];

      }

    }

    else if (isFireFox) {

      for (var i=0; i<jsCssAssets.length; i++) {

        var o =  document.createElement("object");

        o.data = jsCssAssets[i];

        o.width = o.height = 0;

        document.body.appendChild(o);

      }

    }

}



    var onload = function () {

        setTimeout(prefetchTYPAssets, 2000);

    };

    if (window.addEventListener) {

        window.addEventListener("load", onload);

    } else if (window.attachEvent) { /* for <= IE 8 */

        window.attachEvent("onload", onload);

    }

</script>

     <script type="text/javascript">(function ($Nav) {

"use strict";

    return;

}



$Nav.when('$', 'data', 'flyout.yourAccount', 'sidepanel.csYourAccount',

          'config')

    .run("BuyitAgain-YourAccount-SidePanel",

    function ($, data, yaFlyout, csYourAccount, config) {

        if (config.disableBuyItAgain) {

            return;

        }

        var render = function (data) {

            if (data.dramResult) {

                var widgetHtml = data.dramResult;

                navbar.sidePanel({

                    flyoutName: 'yourAccount',

                    data: {html: widgetHtml}

                });

            }

        };



        var renderBuyItAgain = function (biaData) {

            if (csYourAccount) {

                csYourAccount.register(render, biaData);

            } else {

                render(biaData);

            }

        };



        var truncateAndRestructureYaFlyout = function() {

            if (window.P) {

                P.when('A', 'a-truncate').execute(function(A, truncate) {

                    var truncateElements = A.$('.a-truncate');

                    A.each(truncateElements, function(element) {

                        truncate.get(element).update();

                    });

                    var recommendationsWidget = document.getElementById('bia-hcb-widget');

                    if (recommendationsWidget) { 

                        var navFlyout = recommendationsWidget.parentElement;

                        var navFlyoutPaddingBottom = parseInt(window.getComputedStyle(navFlyout).getPropertyValue('padding-bottom'));

                        var navFlyoutContentHeight = navFlyout.clientHeight - navFlyoutPaddingBottom;

                        while (recommendationsWidget.offsetHeight > navFlyoutContentHeight && recommendationsWidget.offsetHeight > 0){

                            var recommendations = recommendationsWidget.querySelectorAll('.biaNavFlyoutFaceout');

                            if (recommendations.length <= 1) {

                                break;

                            }

                            var lastRecommendation = recommendations[recommendations.length - 1];

                            lastRecommendation.parentElement.removeChild(lastRecommendation);

                        }

                    }

               });

            }

        };



        yaFlyout.sidePanel.onData(truncateAndRestructureYaFlyout);

        yaFlyout.onShow(truncateAndRestructureYaFlyout);



    yaFlyout.onRender(function() {

            $.ajax({

                url: '/gp/bia/external/bia-hcb-ajax-handler.html',

                data: {"biaHcbRid":"XBY1VER5YDZ5VY3VPZZA"},

                dataType: 'json',

                timeout: 4*1000,

                success: renderBuyItAgain,

                error: function (jqXHR, textStatus, errorThrown) {

                }

            });

        });

    });

})(window.$Nav);</script>
